{"tid":531841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Sleep is very important ! 每日多睡90分鐘 有助減肥","createTime":"2018-01-17T08:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T09:18:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c447174ae67174af6a017c373a09eadef2a2a165","tid":531841,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"【本報綜合報道】躺着也能減肥？倫敦國王學院一項研究發現，每晚睡眠時間延長九十分鐘或以上，可以減低日間攝取糖分，變相有助減肥。研究學者指出，睡眠有助改變賀爾蒙水平，控制食欲。相反，每日睡眠時間<span style=\"color: red;\">少於七小時者，不但較易肥胖，併發中風、糖尿病</span>等風險亦較高。研究結果刊於《美國臨床營養學》期刊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180117/00176_077.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180117%2F00176_077.html&d=iyvf8w05XlyTyEHPDCLKZP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f86c284e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180117/00176_077.html</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"3f3bf1b82014163dfc4d58741ea8a56a88c34b23","tid":531841,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:39:44.000Z","msg":"more sleep more earn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be341011049ad79dd58bb2fa7f19fa9a32b567c7","tid":531841,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"我訓得少過七粒鐘都係得60kg, 關咩事"},{"pid":"5edf4685a0852a0d884f83d1ad24de57de8d1669","tid":531841,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"啲肥婆瞓幾耐都好<br />\n一餐都超晒標，補返晒"},{"pid":"d5b4c666c47a613b7ccfd7839956c30c2c0eb4f0","tid":531841,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:13:16.000Z","msg":"Sleep is for the weak<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb779a53c4e32448a58ec91963157b93d8fba6e","tid":531841,"uid":20072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"